\mt1 2 TESARONAIKA 
\mt2 Khe Por Phenat…®t…®gap TesaronaikaiŇč Ndi Khergi Gap 
\imt1 Khe fharav gan…®nga buni khare. 
\ip Mbe Tesaronaikan kav guigira Zisasan khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, mbe nd…®knd…®gi vh…®rve ga mbui. Mbe kha nd…®knd…®ga mbui, Krais taagip zir…®rim, thag…®na bigeŇč h…®g…®rie? Mbe mbari khaŇč nzuai, Guma Bak…®me zir…®rga tuk, ana fhum h…®gim, ana zergi. Mbe mba khesharigi nd…®knd…®gi ga mbuim, Por gu Sairas, Timoti, mbe nd…®knd…®gi ndi th…®gar maan zav mba gava khergi. 
\ip Mbe mba gava kherav, Por khaŇč mbe nzuai, mba tuk h…®gi fhuvara. Kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi guigira r…®…®Ňčr…®…®nga, mbark…®rga t…®vi mbat…®gi khaŇč t…®g…® havhargip, kha nuianan h…®rga. Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi dai guma kha nuianan h…®g…®p, guigira panan Krais ga keg…®rga. 
\ip Por th…®g…® havhargip, Zisas khoth…®g…®p simt…®gi ndir zav mba gumgi gu mbigi ga nzuai. Ana khueŇč vuzvugi, mbe th…®g…® havhargip, nduarira wari gan…®nga. Mbe ana phorga Ňčgari gumgi, mbe mbe mbui t…®var muunga. Mbe Ňčaarar vhukvhug…®rga fhu. Mbe vh…®ra harigi nt…®…®rir kurkurargen vhukvhug…®rga fhu. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Guma Bak…®me taagi zir…®rga tuk zumgum h…®rga. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt FG 17.1; 1 Te 1.1\x*Gu Por, Sairas, gu Timoti, nza kha gava khergiap, nde Tesaronaikan Ňčgu bak…®men kav guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi, nza anan nde ndi mbai. Nde nza won Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum nzan Bak…®me Zisas Krais phorga ki gumgi gu mbigi ma. 
\p  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Ro 1.7\x*Nza Ndia Fhe Bak…®me gum nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais, mani nden korar muuŇčv ndava m…®…®t…®gar nden n…®…®Ňčrim, nde k…®ri. 
\s1 Mbe TesaronaikaiŇč, mbe simt…®gi hi tugir, mbe th…®ga havhargi. 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 1 Te 1.2-3; 2 Te 2.13\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nza zazera nde nd…®knd…®gap, nde nzuav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav anan ndikndigi. Nza maaŇč mbui, ne guigira nzerigi. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nde guigira khaŇč t…®gap Zisas khoth…®gap ana z…®n vui ne guigira havhargi. Nde maaŇč mbuav, nde bevbevira wari won ndavi ndiv wari ga nd…®…®i. Nde mba t…®va mbuim, mba t…®v guigira k…®vgi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 1:4 \xt 2 Ko 7.4; 7.14; 1 Te 2.19; VB 1.9\x*Mba big…®na n…®…®eŇčra, nza Fhe Bak…®men siosi ga ruav, nza nde z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuagi. Nza nden pana gumgi nde mbui t…®vi mbat…®gi, nza nta bun mbe nzuav, nden hi simt…®gi, nza vh…®ra nta bun nzuai. Nza mbe nzuav khaŇč nzuai, ‚ÄúTesaronaikaiŇč mbe th…®ga havhargiap, Zisas khoth…®gap, ana z…®n vui t…®va suirav, mben hi simt…®gi gu zaagi, mbe nta ndi.‚ÄĚ 
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me t…®vir vhuuiŇčra z…®n vov, nza mbui t…®vi ga nzuav nza nzuai. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Fi 1.28\x*Mba nden hi bigi, Fhe Bak…®me khuen nza kh…®vigi, ana t…®var vhuuŇčra z…®n vov nza mbui t…®vi ga nzuav, nza nzuai. Nde zaa ndi, ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nde Fhe Bak…®me won gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mbe ana piin k…®rga Ňčgu khavi. Nde maaŇč mbuim, Fhe Bak…®me nde muuŇčgim, nde guigira ana wo gumgi gu mbigi gan…®rim, mba ana piin ki nt…®…®ri, nde mbe phorg…® k…®rga tukt…®gi.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Ro 12.19; VB 18.6-7\x*Fhe Bak…®me t…®var vhuun muuŇčv, khaŇč muunga. Ana simt…®gar nde nd…®…®i gumgi, ana nen Ňčgarkarav simt…®gar mben n…®…®nga.  
\v 7-8 \x - \xo 1:7-8 \xt Mt 25.31; 1 Te 3.13; 4.16\x*\x - \xo 1:7-8 \xt Sng 79.6; Ais 66.15; Jer 10.25; Ro 2.8; 1 Pi 4.17\x*Nde ntige mba ndi simt…®gi, ana nta vh…®zgip, vhuksur nden n…®…®Ňčv, vh…®ra nzan n…®…®nga. Nza Bak…®me Zisas won enseri ŇčkasŇčkagir kov, mbe Hevenan keg…®p, k…®rar h…®rga tugar, Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč muunga. Ana vhava bak…® guarara phorg…® zir…®rga. Ana zir…®v, Fhe Bak…®me kangeŇč thagi gumgi gu mbigi gum, nza Bak…®me Zisas buna vhuueŇč mbararargeŇč thagi gumgi gu mbigi, ana muumbara mbat…®gar mben muuŇčgirga.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 1:9 \xt Ais 2.10; 2.19-21; Fi 3.19; 2 Pi 3.7\x*Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mba khesharigi vheza mbat…®ga ndigirga. Mbe Guma Bak…®me thav, samra k…®rga, mbe vh…®ra, ana vhava Ňčaara ŇčkasŇčka thav, samra k…®v, mbe zazera mbat…®gip mbara muuŇčgip k…®rga.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt Sng 68.35; 89.7; Kor 3.4; 1 Te 3.13\x*Fhe Bak…®me mba sarigi tugar, Guma Bak…®me z…®v muumbara mbat…®gar mben muunga. Mba Fhe Bak…®men gumgi gu mbigi, mbe guigira ana khoth…®gi gumgi gu mbigi ma. Mbe ana z…® ndiv vun kuamkuav, anan ndikndig…®rga. Nde vh…®ra mbe phorg…®p ndikndig…®rga. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nza nde r…®gar kav, Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč bun nde suaŇčgim, nde guigira ne khoth…®gi. 
\s1 Mbe TesaronaikaiŇč havhar…® zav Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuai. 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 1:11 \xt Kor 1.9; 1 Te 1.2-3\x*Nza mba h…®r zav mbui bigi ga nd…®knd…®gap, nza zazera nde nzuav, nza won Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav, anan nzai, ana nden kurkurarga. Nza khueŇč vuzvugi, nde guigira ana muun zav nden kamgi t…®vi, nde ntan muunga. Nza ana ŇčkasŇčkar nden n…®…®n zav, nza ne nzuav ana phorga nzuai. Nde ana khoth…®gi nd…®knd…®k nde ndavi khav…®rim, nde mba muun zav mbui t…®vir vhuuiŇč, nde zam ntan muunga.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Ais 24.15; Mal 1.11; 1 Pi 1.7; 4.14\x*Nde mba t…®var muuŇčv, nza wo Bak…®me Zisas z…® ndiv vun kuamkuarga, ana vh…®ra nde z…®ri ndiv vun kuamkuarga. Nza Fhe Bak…®me gum nza Bak…®me Zisas Krais nden korar muuŇčv, mba t…®var nden muuŇčri. 
\c 2  
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi daai guma h…®g…®rga. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Mt 24.31; 1 Te 4.13-17\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nza ntigem nza wo Bak…®me Zisas Krais taagi zir…®rim, nza ana phorg…®p phogar vhorga ne bun nde suan zav mbui. Nza khueŇč vuzvugi, nde tuituigip khuarir nza kha nzuai bunen t…®g…®ri.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 2:2 \xt Mt 24.4; Ef 5.6; 1 Zo 4.1\x*Gumgi thari khaŇč nde suaŇčgi thi, ‚ÄúGuma Bak…®me zir…®rga tuk h…®gim, ana taagia zergi?‚ÄĚ MaaŇč suaŇčgi guma khueŇč nd…®knd…®gi thi? Fhe Bak…®men Ňäina Ňäaar mba kamen ana n…®…®Ňčgi, ana zumgum h…®rga bigeŇč ana ne bun suaŇčgi o, guma the Fhe Bak…®men buni vhuuiŇč bun nzuav ne bun suaŇčgire? O, guma the khaŇč suaŇčgi, nza kha gava kherav, mba khesharigi kamen nde suaŇčgi. Nde maaŇčgi Ňčanen kha kameŇč mbararagi, ne fhura ki kameŇč ma. Nde ne mbararagip, nde vhemkora Ňčgava mbat…®gar muuŇčv ne suaŇčv sim…® thari.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Zo 17.12; 1 T 4.1; 1 Zo 2.18; 4.3; VB 13.11-14\x*Nde fhura guma the gan…®rim, ana nde guiguigi thari. Ana mbui t…®va thueŇč vh…®ra nde guiguig…® thari. Nde mbarara. Mba tuk fhura h…®g…®rga fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Gumgi vh…®rve, mbe fharav r…®…®Ňčr…®…®Ňčv k…®r Fhe Bak…®me seg…®rga. Mba Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi daasui guma, ana za k…®rar h…®g…®rga. Mba guma, ana Herar k…®v mbar…®g…®rga guma ma.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Dan 7.25; 11.36; Ese 28.2; 1 Ko 8.5; VB 13.6\x*Ana z…®v, mbar…®vi gu tori, ana panan nta keg…®rga. Ana maaŇč muuŇčv, fhura ndikndig…®p nduara wo z…® ndiv vun kuamkuagi bigi, ana zam nta mbevarga. Ana maaŇč muuŇčv, Fhe Bak…®me Phena vhen Ňčgirg…®p perav, khaŇč suanga, ‚ÄúGu nduara Fhe Bak…®me ma.‚ÄĚ 
\p  
\v 5 Gu nde phorga kav mba bigir nde suaŇčgi. Nde nta nd…®knd…®k Ňčangi thi?  
\v 6 Nde ntigem, mba guma k…®rar h…®r za mbuim, ana tuav mp…®rigi big…®n, nde ana kaŇčgi. Ana Fhe Bak…®me ana sarigi tugara, ana h…®rga.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt 1 Zo 2.18; 4.3\x*Nde kaŇčgi, ntigem, Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi daai t…®v, ana zorgap vhee mbugum Ňčgarav ki. Ana mbara muuŇčgip vhen mbugum Ňčgar…®v k…®rim, Fhe Bak…®me farasarigi tuk h…®rga, mba anan tuav mp…®rigi guma, mba tuav thav sarga.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 2:8 \xt Jop 4.9; Ais 11.4; Dan 7.10; Hi 10.27; VB 19.15\x*Mba tugar Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi daai guma za k…®rar h…®g…®rga. Nza Bak…®me Zisas won kamthooŇč b…®…®Ňčb…®…®Ňčra ana shogirim, ana rimgirga. Nza Bak…®me vhemkora won vhava Ňčaara bak…®me phorg…®p k…®rar h…®g…®rga, ana Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi daai guman farfagirga.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt Mt 24.24; Zo 8.41; Ef 2.2; VB 13.11-13; 18.23; 19.20\x*Mba Fhe Bak…®me suaŇčgi t…®vi daai guma, ana Satan ŇčkasŇčkar panan k…®rar h…®g…®rga. Ana k…®rar h…®g…®p, Satan bigi guiguigi t…®var muuŇčv, ana mbark…®rga Ňčaari bak…®vir muuŇčv, mbark…®rga guiguigi mirikori, ana ntan muunga.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt 2 Ko 2.15; 4.3\x*Ana mba guiguigi t…®vi mbat…®gi, ana zam ntan mba za mbar…®girga tuavara vui gumgi gu mbigi, ana mbe guiguigirga. Mba gumgi gu mbigi, mbe mbat…®girga. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, Fhe Bak…®me taagip mbe ndir zav buni guarir mbe n…®…®Ňčgim, mbe mba buni vuzvugi fhu.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Mt 24.5; 24.11; Ro 1.24; 1 T 4.1; 2 T 4.4\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, Fhe Bak…®me mbe nd…®knd…®gi ga muuŇčgim, mbe mba guiguigi buni, mbe nta khoth…®g…®rga.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Ro 1.32\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, mba buni guari khoth…®gi fhuv gumgi gu mbigi, mbe zam t…®vi mbat…®gir muungeŇč nzuav ndikndigi. Mbe Fhe Bak…®me za kha nuianan ki gumgi gu mbigi muuŇčgi t…®vi mbat…®gi ga suaŇčv mbe suanga tugar mbe ne suaŇčv vheza mbat…®ga ndirga. 
\s1 Fhe Bak…®me taagip nde ndir zav nden farasarigi. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Ru 1.75; Zo 15.16; Ef 1.4; 1 Te 4.7; 5.9; 2 Te 1.3\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, Guma Bak…®me guigira wo ndavar nde n…®…®Ňčgi. Nza zazera mba nd…®knd…®gar muuŇčv, nza khueŇč nd…®knd…®g…®rga, nza zazera nde suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v suaŇčv ana ndikndigirga. Fhe Bak…®me fhum guarara nde farasarigi, nde ana ndir za mbui gumgi gu mbigi, r…®gar ki. Fhe Bak…®me won Ňäina Ňäaarar nde n…®…®Ňčgi, nde anan gumgi gu mbigir vhuuiŇč ma. Nde Fhe Bak…®me buna guareŇč khoth…®gim, Fhe Bak…®me maaŇč muuŇčgiap taagia nde ndigi.  
\v 14 Nza mba Fhe Bak…®me buna vhuuen nde suaŇčgi. Fhe Bak…®me mba buna vhuuen panan, ana khueŇč vuzvugiap, nden kamgi, nde vh…®ra nza wo Bak…®me Zisas Kraisan vhava Ňčaara bak…®me gum ana ŇčkasŇčka bak…®me vhen k…®rga.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Ko 11.2; 16.13; Fi 4.1; 2 Te 3.6\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgiap, nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi nde guigira th…®g…® havhargiri. Nde th…®g…® havhargip, nde nza mba Fhe Bak…®me buni vhuuiŇč bun nde suaŇčgi, nde nta suira havhargip, nde vh…®ra nza kha gava khergiap, nde nzuai buni, nde vh…®ra nta suirav havhargiri. 
\p  
\v 16 Fhe Bak…®me won ndavar nzan n…®…®Ňčv, ana nza kora muuŇčgiap, ana nza ndavi vheri ga muuŇčgim, nta zazera nzerara ki. Ana vh…®ra nzan kurkurigim, nza ana khoth…®gap, ana guigira t…®var vhuun nzan muungen rarga ki.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt 1 Ko 1.8; 1 Te 3.13; 1 Pi 5.10\x*Gu maaŇč muuŇčgiap, gu nza Guma Bak…®me Zisas Krais gum nzan Ndia Fhe Bak…®me phorga nzuav manin nzai, mani nde ndavi vherir muuŇčrim, nde ndavi havhargip, nde t…®vir vhuuin muuŇčv bunin vhuuiŇčra suanga. 
\c 3  
\ms1 Mbe TesaronaikaiŇč, mbe vhukvhuga k…®vgi gumgi, mbe mbe nzuav mben t…®vi ndiv th…®gar mbai. 
\s1 Nde Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®v suaŇčrim, ana nzan kurkurari. 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Ef 6.19; Kor 4.3; 1 Te 5.25\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nza nde suanga buna mueŇč phorga khar ki. Mba buneŇč khaŇč muuŇčgi. Nde nza suaŇčv Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčrim, ana nzan kurkurarim, Guma Bak…®me buna vhuueŇč vhemkora za kha bigir Ňčg…®rim, ana z…® guigira k…®vgip, ana nde han maam, nden r…®gar z…® k…®vgi farar muuŇčgirga.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt FG 28.24; Ro 10.16; 15.31\x*Nde vh…®ra Fhe Bak…®me phorg…®p suaŇčrim, ana mba gumgi mbat…®gi farve t…®n nza ndigirga. Mba gumgi, mbe t…®vi mbat…®gi ga mbui gumgi ma. Nde kaŇčgi, gumgi mbari, mbe Krais khoth…®gi fhu. 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Zo 17.15; 1 Ko 1.9; 1 Te 5.24; 2 Pi 2.9\x*Guma Bak…®me, ana wo nzuai buni, ana za nta z…®n vui. Ana nde gan…®v, nden havhargirga, Satan big…®n thuen nden muuŇčgirga tukt…®gi fhu.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 3:4 \xt 2 Ko 7.16; Ga 5.10; 1 Te 4.10\x*Guma Bak…®me nd…®knd…®gar nza nd…®…®im, nza tuituigiap khueŇč kaŇčgi, nza mba muun zav nde suaŇčgi t…®vi, nde zam nta mbui. Nde zumgum vh…®ra mba t…®vara muunga. 
\p  
\v 5 Nza khueŇč vuzvugi, Guma Bak…®me nd…®knd…®gar nden n…®…®Ňčrim, nde nd…®knd…®gi nzerara k…®v, nde Fhe Bak…®me guigira won ndavar kha gumgi gu mbigi ga nd…®…®i t…®v, nde guigira ana kaŇčgip, nde vh…®ra Krais th…®ga havhargiap simt…®gi ndigine, nde vh…®ra ne kaŇčgirga. 
\s1 Gumgi za Ňčgar…®ri. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Mt 18.17; Ro 16.17; 1 Ko 5.11-13; 1 Te 3.11-13; 1 T 6.5; 2 Zo 1.10\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nza wo Guma Bak…®me Zisas Krais z…®n panan, nza khaŇč t…®ga havhargiap, khaŇč nde nzuai. MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guigira nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi thari, mbe fhura piigip k…®v, nza mbe suaŇčgi buni, mbe nta z…®n Ňčg…® thagi, nde mbe thav samra k…®ri.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt 1 Ko 4.16; Fi 3.17; 1 Te 1.6\x*Nde kaŇčgi, nde nza mbui t…®vi z…®n Ňčg…®ri. Nza nde phorga kav, nza fhura piigiap kegi fhuvara.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt 2 Ko 11.9; 1 Te 2.9\x*Nza vh…®ra fhura nden han mba thari ndigi fhuvara. Zak…®ra fhuvara! Nza nde han vhezi. Nza simt…®gar nden n…®…®Ňč thav, nza raa gu maan, nza Ňčaara mbat…®ga muuŇčgi.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt 1 Ko 9.4-6; 1 Te 1.6\x*Nza nden han mba ndi thav, mba Ňčaara muuŇčgi, fhuvara. Nza nde han mba ndirga tukt…®gi, nza nde han mba ndigi fhuvara. Ne khaŇč muuŇčgi, nza nde muunga t…®var vhuuŇč, nza anan nde kh…®vigi, nde nduarira mba t…®va z…®n Ňčg…®ri. 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt 1 Te 4.11\x*Nde kaŇčgi, nza nde phorgara kav, nza kha kamen nde suaŇčgi, maaŇč muuŇčgip, guma Ňčaara thagi, nde mban ana n…®…®Ňč thari.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 3:11 \xt 1 T 5.13; 1 Pi 4.15\x*Nza ntigem mbararagi, nde mbari fhura piigiap ki. Mbe Ňčgari fhu, mbe fhura ka harigi gumgi muuŇčgi bigi, mbe nta neŇčga rui.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt 1 Te 4.11\x*Nza ntigem Guma Bak…®me Zisas Kraisan z…®n panan, nza kama havharar khaŇč mba gumgi ga nzuai, mbe tuituigiap piigip Ňčgar…®ri. Mbe Ňčgar…®p, nduarira mban wari gan…®ri. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Ga 6.9\x*Nde nza phorgap guigira Zisas khoth…®gi gumgi, nde t…®var vhuun muungen vhukvhug…® thari.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt 1 Ko 5.9-11\x*MaaŇč muuŇčgip, guma the nza kha khergi gavara ki buni, ana zam nta z…®n vui fhu, nde mba guma gangip, ana hiav, nde ana thav, samra k…®ri. Nde samra k…®rim, ana nde gangip, ana wo mbui t…®var mbergirga.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 3:15 \xt 1 Te 5.14; Ta 3.10\x*Nza kha nd…®knd…®gar anan muun zav nde nzuai fhuvara, ana nden pana guma ma. Fhuvara. Nde kha nd…®knd…®gar ana muuŇčri, ana nde phorge r…®gine ma. Nde mba nd…®knd…®gar ana muuŇčv, nde nd…®knd…®ga vhuun ana nd…®…®i bunin ana suaŇčri. 
\s1 Por won raar vhuun mbe nd…®…®i. 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt 1 Te 5.23\x*Guma Bak…®me, ana ndava m…®…®t…®gar n…®…®Ňčge ma. Ana zazera nden kurkurarim, nde za bigir muuŇčv ndavi mb…®rav k…®rga. Guma Bak…®me zam nde phorg…® k…®ri. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt 1 Ko 16.21\x*Gu Por, gu nduara kha raar vhuun nde nd…®…®i kameŇč khergiap, nde ndi mbai. Gu wo gavi kherav, nta ndi mbav, gu zazera nduara won raar vhuuŇč kherav, ntan ndi mbai. Nde gu khergi gavi gan…®nga, nde nan Ňčkeeri gan…®nga, nta za gu khergi gavir ki. 
\p  
